data.description: Like new and spacious at over 1700 square foot this home rests within close proximity to NEA BAPTIST Hospital and Arkansas State University. The corner lot location is sure to please. Inside you immediately are drawn to the airy cleanliness, beautiful flooring. color scheme and space.     The split floor plan features 2 large bedrooms with walk in closets and a full bathroom on one side of the home with the oversized master suite on the other. The kitchen boasts gray cabinets set off by white solid surface countertops and stainless appliances. There is also a pantry, island, and ample space for formal dining. Outside is a large fully fenced backyard and a true 2 car garage. This home is priced to sell and waiting for you.
